5-Star_Outrider.name: 5-Star Outrider
5-Star_Outrider.description: Amber's outfit. An Outrider's uniform made for maximum mobility.

All_Is_Overt_Through_My_Lens.name: "All Is Overt Through My Lens"
All_Is_Overt_Through_My_Lens.description: Charlotte's outfit. "If your reporting isn't real enough, it's because you're not close enough.
But of course, maybe it's that the lens you're using just isn't that great."

Aratakis_Demonic_Deputy.name: Arataki's Demonic Deputy
Aratakis_Demonic_Deputy.description: Kuki Shinobu's outfit. The iconic oni mask she wears symbolizes her role as the Arataki Gang's terrifying "demonic deputy."

A_New_Leaf.name: A New Leaf
A_New_Leaf.description: Collei's outfit. Now that she no longer needs to remain bundled in a thick cloak, she is free to emerge like a newly-sprouted leaf and welcome every lovely sunrise.

A_Wrathful_Void.name: A Wrathful Void
A_Wrathful_Void.description: Wanderer's outfit. An ascetic's garb and hat can provide the wanderer some shelter from the rain, but they can do nothing to quell the winds and storms raging within.

Ardent_Soul.name: Ardent Soul
Ardent_Soul.description: Xinyan's outfit. A rocker's stage costume adorned with spikes.

Armored_Rose.name: Armored Rose
Armored_Rose.description: Noelle's outfit. Heavy clothing made of durable velvet and metal plates.

Azure_Silk.name: Azure Silk
Azure_Silk.description: Xingqiu's outfit. Fine robes woven from the high-quality silk sold by the Feiyun Commerce Guild.

Blades_of_Glory.name: Blades of Glory
Blades_of_Glory.description: Tartaglia's outfit. Illustrious attire that signifies Childe's position as the eleventh Fatui Harbinger.

Breezy_Ode.name: Breezy Ode
Breezy_Ode.description: Venti's outfit. The clothes of a carefree bard.

Cherubic_Osmanthus.name: Cherubic Osmanthus
Cherubic_Osmanthus.description: Yaoyao's outfit. A lovely, short jacket Yaoyao's parents made for her. As the little girl travels safely between Qingce Village and Liyue Harbor, this jacket, along with the adeptal bells her master gave her, always keeps her company.

Clear_Adjudication.name: Clear Adjudication
Clear_Adjudication.description: Neuvillette's outfit. The solemn, elegant garb of the Iudex. The complexity in its design does, in fact, cause some inconveniences in movement, but to its wearer, that it matches his standing is a more important matter.

Coronated_Prima_Donna.name: Coronated Prima Donna
Coronated_Prima_Donna.description: Furina's outfit. When the curtain rises, the star of the show is meant to shine bright on the stage, and even gorgeous costumes adorned with diamonds pale in comparison to her own dazzling brilliance.

Darknight_Blaze.name: Darknight Blaze
Darknight_Blaze.description: Diluc's outfit. A smart and tasteful suit fit for a nobleman.

Desert_and_Night.name: Desert and Night
Desert_and_Night.description: Candace's outfit. No matter where she goes, the golden sands and the nights of her homeland that adorn her clothes go together with her.

Dreaming_Star.name: Dreaming Star
Dreaming_Star.description: Layla's outfit. In the depths of quiet nights, the stars that dot the sky wrap her like a cloak, guiding her into sweet dreams - well, or so she dearly wishes might happen.

Dunkelnacht_Sakrament.name: Dunkelnacht Sakrament
Dunkelnacht_Sakrament.description: Fischl's outfit. The Prinzessin der Verurteilung's customary vestments during her sojourn upon this realm.

Eccentric_Oni.name: Eccentric Oni
Eccentric_Oni.description: Itto's outfit. It has an uncommon air of awesomeness about it, and the oni mask worn at the hip is quite imposing indeed — certainly enough to reduce even the naughtiest child of Hanamizaka to terrified tears.

Endurer_of_Eons.name: Endurer of Eons
Endurer_of_Eons.description: Xiao's outfit. Classical battle-wear fit for a thousand years of evil-conquering.

Executors_Thorns.name: Executor's Thorns
Executors_Thorns.description: Rosaria's outfit. Rosaria has heavily modified this particular Church of Favonius uniform.

Falling_Leaves.name: Falling Leaves
Falling_Leaves.description: Kaedehara Kazuha's outfit. The maple leaf patterns are the hallmark of this wandering samurai's clothes.

Fantasticat.name: Fantasticat
Fantasticat.description: Lyney's outfit. Cats only stretch in front of those they trust completely. Otherwise, they merely hide their claws behind a smile — intimate yet reserved, just like the sweet words of this magician.

Favonian_Devotion.name: Favonian Devotion
Favonian_Devotion.description: Jean's outfit. Neat and smart clothing that emphasizes her chivalry.

Flawless_Radiance.name: Flawless Radiance
Flawless_Radiance.description: Kamisato Ayaka's outfit. This kimono features an armor-coated skirt, displaying the nobility and resilience of the Shirasagi Himegimi.

Flowing_Fate.name: Flowing Fate
Flowing_Fate.description: Mona's outfit. A light astrologist's outfit that does away with superfluous fabric to provide top quality at an affordable price.

For_All_Knowledge_a_Verse.name: For All Knowledge, a Verse
For_All_Knowledge_a_Verse.description: Nahida's outfit. Only the oracles that interpret knowledge may robe the God of Wisdom, and so even the smallest ornament is viewed by believers as holy writ.

Fortunes_Favor.name: Fortune's Favor
Fortunes_Favor.description: Bennett's outfit. An old adventurer's uniform that has been patched and sewn up in various places.

Frostdew_Trail.name: Frostdew Trail
Frostdew_Trail.description: Ganyu's outfit. Elegant clothes blessed by the mighty and illuminated adepti.

Germinating_Wind.name: Germinating Wind
Germinating_Wind.description: Sucrose's outfit. A Knights of Favonius alchemist's uniform customized for Sucrose.

Gold_Leaf_and_Pearly_Jade.name: Gold Leaf and Pearly Jade
Gold_Leaf_and_Pearly_Jade.description: Ningguang's outfit. Intricate embroidery is the hallmark of this graceful dress.

Gold_Pinions_in_Flames_Bathed.name: Gold Pinions in Flames Bathed
Gold_Pinions_in_Flames_Bathed.description: Kaveh's outfit. A notable tailor from Treasures Street created these clothes in imitation of the lovely sight of birds extending their wings in flight and would only sell them to those who knew how to appreciate their beauty.

Golden_Rule.name: Golden Rule
Golden_Rule.description: Yanfei's outfit. The dress that the legal adviser Yanfei wears when she heads out to visit clients.

Goldfish_Firecracker.name: Goldfish Firecracker
Goldfish_Firecracker.description: Yoimiya's outfit. A patchwork of memories from festivals over the years.

Heart_of_the_Scales.name: Heart of the Scales
Heart_of_the_Scales.description: Cyno's outfit. This garb displays the General Mahamatra's dignity and the just principles he sticks by. It was a rather complicated piece to commission due to Cyno's request for the custom-made head ornaments and requires regular maintenance.

Hermit_of_Mortal_Life.name: Hermit of Mortal Life
Hermit_of_Mortal_Life.description: Zhongli's outfit. This is the leisurewear of choice for Zhongli, the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor's consultant.

I_Love_Mora.name: I Love Mora
I_Love_Mora.description: Dori's outfit. This outfit almost begs to be further adorned with gems and precious metals, loudly announcing its wearer's love of wealth to the world. And they say that this is the merchant Dori's casual wear... So does this mean that she has clothes even more expensive than this one!?

Icy_Featherflight.name: Icy Featherflight
Icy_Featherflight.description: Kaeya's outfit. Fashionable clothes festooned with a fur collar.

Icy_Skin.name: Icy Skin
Icy_Skin.description: Freminet's outfit. This suit wraps around the deep diver like a second skin, his constant companion in countless sallies to the silent seabed.

Innocent_Longing.name: Innocent Longing
Innocent_Longing.description: Barbara's outfit. A Deaconess's uniform from the Church of Favonius with a unique Barbara streak running through it.

Machine_Hunter.name: Machine Hunter
Machine_Hunter.description: Aloy's outfit. A hunter's garb suited to life in the wilds.

Mikos_Instruction.name: Miko's Instruction
Mikos_Instruction.description: Yae Miko's outfit. A shrine maiden uniform that declares her lofty position as the Guuji of the Grand Narukami Shrine to all. May the lovely sight of her in that dress remain forever, just as the Sacred Sakura emblazoned upon her pure white skirt, which will never wilt away.

Mini_Mujina.name: Mini Mujina
Mini_Mujina.description: Sayu's outfit. Marvelous attire designed after the mysterious animal known as the Mujina.

Mistcloud_Stage.name: Mistcloud Stage
Mistcloud_Stage.description: Yun Jin's outfit. It was made by skilled tailors from the Feiyun Commerce Guild. Yun Jin fell in love with it at first sight, and it is now her favorite set of casual wear.

Narukamis_Law.name: Narukami's Law
Narukamis_Law.description: The Raiden Shogun's outfit. This kimono has been adorned with the Electro Mitsudomoe, granting it the highest honor in the land.

Neither_Flower_Nor_Mist.name: Neither Flower Nor Mist
Neither_Flower_Nor_Mist.description: Nilou's outfit. It is neither flower nor mist, but when she begins to dance, both seem to bloom into being.

Newmoon_Starlight.name: Newmoon Starlight
Newmoon_Starlight.description: Albedo's outfit. The Knights of Favonius alchemist's uniform that Albedo often wears when conducting his experiments.

Nights_Chilling_Howl.name: Night's Chilling Howl
Nights_Chilling_Howl.description: Wriothesley's outfit. It radiates both dignity and strength, with the rugged gray wolf chain serving as the mark of his rulership over the Fortress of Meropide.

Panoply_of_a_Hundred_Hunts.name: Panoply of a Hundred Hunts
Panoply_of_a_Hundred_Hunts.description: Gorou's outfit. This light armor is designed to allow the marksman-general Gorou to handle his bow with ease. The armoring at the shoulder and elbow is also designed with this in mind.

Phantomeow.name: Phantomeow
Phantomeow.description: Lynette's outfit. A cat resides in the shadows until it wishes to show itself — inscrutable, just like a magician's assistant.

Piercing_Thunderbolt.name: Piercing Thunderbolt
Piercing_Thunderbolt.description: Keqing's outfit. A formidable-looking dress made using luxurious materials.

Plum_Blossom_Bouquet.name: Plum Blossom Bouquet
Plum_Blossom_Bouquet.description: Hu Tao's outfit. The daily work clothes of the Wangsheng Funeral Parlor's director.

Pristine_Elegance.name: Pristine Elegance
Pristine_Elegance.description: Faruzan's outfit. The relatively plain yet elegant style represents her unfaltering purity. This style was very popular in the Akademiya a hundred years ago, but has now become an uncommon sight.

Pure_Spirit.name: Pure Spirit
Pure_Spirit.description: Chongyun's outfit. A traditional thaumaturge's trappings.

Purple_Rose.name: Purple Rose
Purple_Rose.description: Lisa's outfit. A slim-fit dress adorned with roses that displays a young lady's elegance.

Red_Pepper_and_Turmeric.name: Red Pepper and Turmeric
Red_Pepper_and_Turmeric.description: Xiangling's outfit. Light and comfortable clothing brimming with fiery passion.

Rising_Star_Female.name: Rising Star (Lumine)
Rising_Star_Female.description: The Traveler's outfit. A practical set of clothing to wear during a long journey.

Rising_Star_Male.name: Rising Star (Aether)
Rising_Star_Male.description: The Traveler's outfit. A practical set of clothing to wear during a long journey.

Rolling_Waves.name: Rolling Waves
Rolling_Waves.description: Beidou's outfit. Lightweight clothing saturated with a brave seafarer's spirit.

Shooting_Spark.name: Shooting Spark
Shooting_Spark.description: Klee's outfit. A set of clothing for an energetic child that even comes with a matching leather backpack.

Silk_Splendor.name: Silk Splendor
Silk_Splendor.description: Kamisato Ayato's outfit. The kimono itself is made using uncommon fabrics, and its patterning recalls a mountain spring, giving off a feeling of calm and stability that matches its wearer.

Soaring_Beacon.name: Soaring Beacon
Soaring_Beacon.description: Mika's outfit. This knightly outfit, specially designed for field work, is made using a vast multitude of flexible but tough materials, adding plenty of places for the wearer to store his weapons and tools. Dressed and prepared, fortune is certain to stride alongside the wearer of this outfit with each step into the unknown.

Solemn_Purity.name: Solemn Purity
Solemn_Purity.description: Kujou Sara's outfit. Prim and proper, it is a garment worthy of an Archon's devout servant.

Sparkling_Coralbone.name: Sparkling Coralbone
Sparkling_Coralbone.description: Sangonomiya Kokomi's outfit. A noble's dress decorated with little precious objects produced in Watatsumi Island.

Spirited_Valor.name: Spirited Valor
Spirited_Valor.description: Shikanoin Heizou's outfit style. Having taken his outer coat off and tucked it around his waist, the Tenryou Commission detective cuts quite the dashing figure.

Sugary_Brew.name: Sugary Brew
Sugary_Brew.description: Diona's outfit. The work uniform of the Cat's Tail's star bartender.

Summerchill_Dreams.name: Summerchill Dreams
Summerchill_Dreams.description: Qiqi's outfit. A herb gatherer's garment that brings her great peace of mind due to the attached talismans.

The_Applications_of_Medicine.name: The Applications of Medicine
The_Applications_of_Medicine.description: Baizhu's outfit. The cloak on his shoulder is dyed using Changsheng's favorite plants. Its fragrance lingers and soothes the senses.

The_Lioness_and_the_Blazing_Sun.name: The Lioness and the Blazing Sun
The_Lioness_and_the_Blazing_Sun.description:
Dehya's outfit. It is said when the lion roars, even the scorching sun will quiver.
Though Dehya is long past the age of believing in such stories, it doesn't stop her from gazing upon the sun sinking below the sands, reminiscing about the tales and storytellers of her childhood.

The_Rational.name: The Rational
The_Rational.description:
Alhaitam's outfit. "Don't bother the Scribe with trivialities... What do you think those soundproofers of his are for, anyway?"
So observed an experienced staff member at the Temple of Silence.

The_Waning_Point.name: The Waning Point
The_Waning_Point.description: Yelan's outfit. It has lurked alongside its wearer in the shadows over many a year, to the point where the outfit almost has a mysterious temper of its own, like an orchid blooming at midnight.

The_Worlds_Shackles.name: The World's Shackles
The_Worlds_Shackles.description: Shenhe's outfit. These elegant garments have accompanied her through long years of training. The red ropes that surround her body are fetters and wards simultaneously.

Warrior_of_Flame.name: Warrior of Flame
Warrior_of_Flame.description: Thoma's outfit. He cropped the pieces of this light suit of armor till only the thigh and arm guards were left, allowing him to comfortably attend to all matters in and out of combat.

Wavecrest_Waltz.name: Wavecrest Waltz
Wavecrest_Waltz.description: Eula's outfit. Consummate elegance shines through in this neat and smart knight's uniform.

Whirling_Bloom.name: Whirling Bloom
Whirling_Bloom.description: Kirara's outfit. The famous designer Chiori followed the principle of "comfortably wearing a beautiful flower upon one's body" when creating this outfit for Kirara.

Wild_Sprint.name: Wild Sprint
Wild_Sprint.description: Razor's outfit. Rough and ready clothes suited for running out in the wilderness.

Woodland_Song.name: Woodland Song
Woodland_Song.description: Tighnari's outfit. Clad in the colors of wood, tree, and flower, Tighnari is surrounded at all times by natural life, determined even in fashion sense to put the "forest" in "Forest Watcher."
